1083
01:33:47,211 --> 01:33:48,420
- Adiós.
- Gracias.

1084
01:33:48,420 --> 01:33:49,505
A vosotros.

1085
01:33:50,214 --> 01:33:51,340
Gracias.

1086
01:33:53,592 --> 01:33:56,345
